m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: This +1 dwarven urgrosh grants its wielder a +1 {g|Encyclopedia:Bonus}bonus{/g} on {g|Encyclopedia:Attack}attack rolls{/g} against magical beasts.

Whenever this holy dwarven urgrosh lands a hit but doesn't deal any {g|Encyclopedia:Physical_Damage}physical damage{/g}, the next hit deals force {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage{/g} instead of the normal {g|Encyclopedia:Damage_Type}piercing{/g} or slashing weapon damage.
Whenever this +2 radiant dwarven urgrosh confirms a {g|Encyclopedia:Critical}critical hit{/g}, it deals additional {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}4d6{/g} holy {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage{/g}.

Whenever the wielder of this +5 flaming dwarven urgrosh lands a hit on a new enemy for the first time, the enemy suffers a -2 {g|Encyclopedia:Penalty}penalty{/g} on all {g|Encyclopedia:Saving_Throw}saves{/g} for 4 {g|Encyclopedia:Combat_Round}rounds{/g}. While under this effect, any failed save by the enemy makes it suffer {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}3d6{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:Energy_Damage}fire damage{/g}.

This +5 keen construct bane dwarven urgrosh grants its wielder a +6 insight {g|Encyclopedia:Bonus}bonus{/g} on {g|Encyclopedia:Initiative}Initiative{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}rolls{/g}, increases base {g|Encyclopedia:Speed}speed{/g} by 10 feet and grants a +2 dodge bonus to {g|Encyclopedia:Armor_Class}AC{/g} against Huge and bigger enemies.
This is a +1 cold iron ghost touch weapon.

This is a +3 brilliant energy heartseeker weapon. This weapon can tear the soul of a living enemy: whenever it lands a hit, it deals additional {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}1d6{/g} force {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage{/g}.

m_FlavorText.LocalisedValue: This weapon was once the seat of Finnean's soul. Now that the soul of the Sarkorian Pathfinder has left the weapon, it has fallen silent forever.
